result.execSummary:
The defendant Heather Ashley Paquin was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Heather Ashley Paquin is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.
